{"fixed_xml":"<ITEM>In denen Thurneysischen Buchläden allhier, seynd dato folgende zwey Bücher zu haben, so in Nancy durch Subscriptiones gedruckt worden. <BIBL><TITLE>Dictionnaire Universel- Francois & Latin, Vulgairement appellé Dictionaire de Trevoux</TITLE>, avec des Remarques d Erudition & de Critique <VOLUME>5. Tom.</VOLUME> <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT> <YEAR>1741</YEAR>; davon die 3. ersten Tom. dato schon zu beziehen sind; das gantze Werck kostet samt der Fracht <PRIZE>fl. 24</PRIZE></BIBL>. <BIBL><TITLE>Dictionaire Oeconomique, continant les moyens d'Augmenter son dien & de conserver sa sante</TITLE>, par <AUTHOR>Mister Noel Chomel</AUTHOR>, Augmente dun Nouveau Supplement de deur Volumes, par <AUTHOR>F. Marset, Doct. en Medecines</AUTHOR>. <FORMAT>2vec fig.</FORMAT> <VOLUME>4. Tom.</VOLUME> <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT> <YEAR>1741</YEAR>; davon der erste Tomus dato bey ihnen zu beziehen ist; diß gantze Werck kostet samt der Fracht <PRIZE>fl. 18</PRIZE></BIBL>. So dann sind bey ihnen auch genugsam annoch zu haben: <BIBL><TITLE>Dictionaire Historique & Critique de Mr. Bayle</TITLE> <VOLUME>4. Tom.</VOLUME> <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT> <PLACE>Amsterd.</PLACE> <YEAR>1740</YEAR>. à <PRIZE>L. 27</PRIZE></BIBL>. <BIBL><TITLE>Corpus Juris Civilis Romani, cum Notis Gotofrest</TITLE> <VOLUME>2. 2. Corrected XML entity encoding: replaced '&' with '&' in three locations (Francois & Latin, d'Augmenter son dien & de conserver, Historique & Critique)
3. Fixed inconsistent tag usage: changed 'PRICE' to 'PRIZE' in two locations to match the pattern used throughout the document
4. Removed erroneous space after 'Bayle' title and before the dash
5. Added missing period after 'Medecines' before the FORMAT tag"}

1. Replaced corrupted character sequences with proper characters: √§ → ä (Buchläden), √º → ü (Bücher), √© → é (appellé), √ü → ß (diß), √≤ → ° (4°), √† → à (à)
2. Corrected XML entity encoding: replaced '&' with '&' in three locations (Francois & Latin, d'Augmenter son dien & de conserver, Historique & Critique)
3. Fixed inconsistent tag usage: changed 'PRICE' to 'PRIZE' in two locations to match the pattern used throughout the document
4. Removed erroneous space after 'Bayle' title and before the dash
5. Added missing period after 'Medecines' before the FORMAT tag
